short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Highlights Google Ads within Google search results in order to mitigate the risk of malicious Google Ads through user education.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Draws attention to Google search results that are sponsored without blocking access or changing any other functionality of the browser, allowing a user to click through the ads if they so wish.
